@startuml
title Player UML

left to right direction
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 55

package "Player Core" {
  class PlayerController {
    - movement
    - facing
    - aimPivot
    - playerInput
    - dodge
    - rayInteract
    - holdingItem
    - inventory
    - attack
    - filterInteract
    - dir
    - isfiring
    + OnMove()
    + OnAim()
    + OnFire()
    + OnDodge()
    + OnInteract()
    + OnHoldItem()
    + UseConsumable()
  }

  class Movement {
    + SetMoveInput()
    + GetMoveInput()
    + GetDirection()
    + StopMovement()
    + EnableMovement()
    + DisableMovement()
  }

  class Facing2D {
    + IsFacingRight
    + SetDirection()
  }

  class AimPivot2D {
    + SetDirection()
    + ResetRotation()
  }

  class Attack {
    + TryAttack()
    + RefreshWeapon()
  }

  class Dodge {
    + OnDodge
    + TryDodge()
  }

  class PlayerHealth {
    + Heal()
  }
}

package "Interaction" {
  class RayInteract {
    + target
    + FindClosestItem()
  }

  class FilterInteract {
    + FilterAndExecute()
    + GetInteractionType()
  }
}

package "Inventory" {
  class HoldingWeapon {
    + currentItem
    + currentIndex
    + SetDirection()
    + SetHoldingWeapon()
  }

  class Inventory {
    + Weapons
    + Consumables
    + Coins
    + AddWeapon()
    + DropWeapon()
    + AddConsumable()
    + DropConsumable()
    + AddCoins()
    + SpendCoins()
  }

  class Item {
    + itemData
    + Use()
  }
}

package "Input / Support" {
  class PlayerInput
  class Camera
  class PlayerAnimations {
    + TriggerDodgeAnimation()
  }
}

PlayerInput -left-> PlayerController : input
Camera -left-> PlayerController : mouse aim

PlayerController -right-> Movement : move
PlayerController -right-> Facing2D : face
PlayerController -right-> AimPivot2D : aim
PlayerController -right-> Attack : fire
PlayerController -right-> Dodge : dodge
PlayerController -right-> PlayerHealth : hp

PlayerController -down-> RayInteract : detect target
RayInteract -right-> FilterInteract : pass target

PlayerController --> HoldingWeapon : switch weapon
PlayerController --> Inventory : use consumable

HoldingWeapon --> Inventory : read weapons
Inventory --> Item : contains
PlayerAnimations --> Dodge : subscribe OnDodge
Dodge --> Movement : temporary disable

PlayerInput -[hidden]down- Camera
Camera -[hidden]right- PlayerController
PlayerController -[hidden]right- Movement
Movement -[hidden]down- Facing2D
Facing2D -[hidden]down- AimPivot2D
AimPivot2D -[hidden]down- Attack
Attack -[hidden]down- Dodge
Dodge -[hidden]down- PlayerHealth
RayInteract -[hidden]right- FilterInteract
HoldingWeapon -[hidden]right- Inventory
Inventory -[hidden]down- Item
PlayerAnimations -[hidden]left- Camera

note top of PlayerController
Main orchestrator of the player.
Receives input and delegates work
to movement, combat, interaction,
inventory, and health systems.
end note

note right of RayInteract
Searches the closest
interactable target.
end note

note right of HoldingWeapon
Chooses the current weapon
from Inventory.
end note

note bottom of Dodge
Works together with Movement
and PlayerAnimations for roll flow.
end note

@enduml
